hello!
this is the description for a round textured crochet doily called “arya”.
the pdf file includes:
•	written instructions for each round with a detailed explanation of all special stitches;
•	chart for each round;
•	step by step photo tutorial.
more details:
•	the pattern uses russia terminology;
•	difficulty level: advanced;
•	the pattern consists of 25 rounds;
•	recommended materials: size 10 cotton thread and hook 1.50 mm;
•	using the recommended materials, this pattern will take approximately 240-350 m of thread, the finished doily will be approximately 32 sm after blocking; 
•	stitches and terms used: fp/bp stitches, popcorns, puff stitches, clusters, crab stitch, picot. 
